name: Custom Design-Work Deposit
description:
We must hold a $50 deposit before we begin the design process on your custom work. Pick your theme/imagery and we'll make you your own one-of-a-kind stationery, note, card, invitation, announcement or letter set! Just make your first deposit and then e-mail us your design & color preferences, as well as the quantity to rebeccanolteart@gmail.com. 

Each piece is printed on eco-friendly paper, using high quality archival inks.

Due to the attention to detail we pay to each piece, please allow for at least 4 weeks for all custom orders (from creation to shipment).
